    anchor: aquarium
    title: (Re)download the Aquarium app
    body: |
      The aquarium app is not pre-installed on a new car and needs to be reinstalled if the infotainment system is reset.

      Once installed, you'll find it in "All Apps" and then "Aquarium".

      The car needs a Wi-Fi connection to download the app. Go to "General Settings", "Connections", "Wi-Fi" to set one up if you haven't. ([[manual 307]].) Connect it to e.g. your home Wi-Fi or your phone's hotspot.

      In the car, go to "All Apps" and then "Honda App Center", then download it through there. ([[manual 305]].)

