    anchor: park-a-while
    title: Leave your car parked for a while
    body: |
      Leaving your car at the airport? Thankfully, charging losses when parked seem small.

      There have been reports of losing 0% when parked for a week, and 3% when parked for a 4 weeks. ([Source](https://www.facebook.com/groups/HondaeUK/posts/3234230593499074/). [Source](https://www.facebook.com/groups/HondaeUK/posts/3099402523648549/).)

      Make sure to deactivate any preconditioning schedule since that will use up some charge.

